WishCare’s 5% Niacinamide Oil Balance Fluid Sunscreen SPF 50 PA++++ is a lightweight, non-comedogenic sunscreen specifically formulated for oily and acne-prone skin. It offers broad-spectrum protection against UVA and UVB rays, helping to prevent sunburn, premature aging, and hyperpigmentation. ￼

This sunscreen features a fluid, semi-matte texture that absorbs quickly, leaving no white cast. Its lightweight and non-sticky formula makes it suitable for daily use under makeup or alone. ￼

Apply generously on cleansed face and neck 15-20 minutes before sun exposure. Reapply every two hours, especially after swimming or sweating, to maintain optimal sun protection.

In summary, WishCare’s 5% Niacinamide Oil Balance Fluid Sunscreen SPF 50 PA++++ provides effective sun protection while addressing the specific needs of oily and acne-prone skin, promoting a clear, matte complexion.
